snippet.title: The Lord of the Rings™: Gollum™ | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Embark on a perilous journey as Gollum throughout the lands of Middle-earth.

But two minds in one body won't make for an easy quest…

The Lord of the Rings™: Gollum™ will be available in 2022 on Xbox and PlayStation consoles, Nintendo Switch™ and PC.
